ed="T" n="0834a07"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0834a07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>南嶽山<persName key="A010199">明瓚</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0834a08"/><persName key="A010199">釋明瓚</persName>者，未知氏族生緣。初遊方詣<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩山</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0834a09"/><persName key="A009319">普寂</persName>盛行禪法，<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>往從焉。然則默證<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>之心<lb
ed="T" n="0834a10"/>契，人罕推重。尋於<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡巖</placeName>閑居，眾僧營作，我<lb
ed="T" n="0834a11"/>則晏如，縱被詆訶，殊無愧恥，時目之<persName key="A010199">懶瓚</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0834a12"/>也。一說伊僧差越等夷<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g630"/>，或隨眾齋飡，或以<lb
ed="T" n="0834a13"/>瓦釜煮土而食，云是彌陀佛應身，未知何<lb
ed="T" n="0834a14"/>證驗之？一<anchor xml:id="beg0834sgsz7"/>云<anchor xml:id="end0834sgsz7"/>好食僧之殘食，故殘也（殘上聲呼）。或<lb
ed="T" n="0834a15"/>隨逐之，則時出言語，皆契佛理，事迹難知。<lb
ed="T" n="0834a16"/><date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141993438" notAfter-iso="+0745-09-30"><name>天寶</name>初</date>，至<placeName key="PL000000028989">南嶽寺</placeName>執役，<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>盡</sic><corr>晝</corr></choice>專一寺之<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>上</sic><corr>工</corr></choice><ptr target="#n562"/>，夜<lb
ed="T" n="0834a17"/>止群牛之下，曾無倦也。如是經二十年。相<lb
ed="T" n="0834a18"/>國鄴公<persName key="A009805">李泌</persName>避<persName key="A012436">崔</persName>、<persName key="A008840">李</persName>之害，隱<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>而潛察<lb
ed="T" n="0834a19"/><persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>所為，曰：「非常人也。」聽其中<anchor xml:id="beg0834001"/>宵<anchor xml:id="end0834001"/><name>梵</name>唄，響徹<lb
ed="T" n="0834a20"/>山谷。<persName key="A009805">李公</persName>情頗知音，能辯休戚，謂<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>曰「經<lb
ed="T" n="0834a21"/>音悽愴而後喜悅，必讁墮之人時將去矣。」候<lb
ed="T" n="0834a22"/>中夜，<persName key="A009805">李公</persName>潛往謁焉，望席門自贊而拜。<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0834a23"/>大詬，仰空而唾曰：「是將賊我。」<persName key="A009805">李</persName>愈加鄭重，<lb
ed="T" n="0834a24"/>唯拜而已。<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>正發牛糞火，出芋啗之，良久乃<lb
ed="T" n="0834a25"/>曰：「可以席地。」取所啗芋之半以授焉。<persName key="A009805">李</persName>跪<lb
ed="T" n="0834a26"/>捧盡食而謝。謂<persName key="A009805">李公</persName>曰：「慎勿多言，領取十<lb
ed="T" n="0834a27"/>年宰相。」<persName key="A009805">李</persName>拜而退。居一月，<anchor xml:id="beg0834002"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0834002"/>史祭岳，修道<lb
ed="T" n="0834a28"/>路極嚴。忽中夜風雷，而一峯頹下，其緣山蹬<lb
ed="T" n="0834a29"/>道為大石所攔，乃以數牛<ptr target="#n564"/>縻絆而挽之，又<pb ed="T" n="0834b" xml:id="T50.2061.0834b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0834b01"/>以數百人鼓噪以推之，物力竭而石愈固，<lb
ed="T" n="0834b02"/>更無他術。<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>曰：「奚用如許繁為？<persName key="A010199">我</persName>始去之。<ptr target="#n566"/>」<lb
ed="T" n="0834b03"/>眾皆大笑，<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>遂履石而動，忽轉盤而下，聲<lb
ed="T" n="0834b04"/>若震雷。山路既開，眾僧<anchor xml:id="beg0834sgsz10"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0834sgsz10"/>而踴躍，一郡呼<lb
ed="T" n="0834b05"/>為至聖，太守奉如神明。<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>悄然乃懷去意。<lb
ed="T" n="0834b06"/>寺外虎豹忽爾成群，日有殺傷，無由禁止。<lb
ed="T" n="0834b07"/><persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>曰：「授<persName key="A010199">我</persName>一小<anchor xml:id="beg0834sgsz12"/>箠<anchor xml:id="end0834sgsz12"/>，為爾驅除。」眾曰：「大石猶<lb
ed="T" n="0834b08"/>可推，虎豹當易制。」遂與之荊梃，皆躡後以<lb
ed="T" n="0834b09"/>觀之。出門，見一虎銜之而去。<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>既去矣，虎<lb
ed="T" n="0834b10"/>亦絕蹤矣。<persName key="A009805">李鄴公</persName>於<date notBefore-iso="+0752-12-30" key="j19960861997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name>末</date>，<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>北巡，至<lb
ed="T" n="0834b11"/><placeName key="PL000000047120">靈武</placeName>即位，遣使訪召。會<persName key="A009805">泌</persName>自嵩<placeName key="PL000000023277">頴</placeName>奔赴行<lb
ed="T" n="0834b12"/>在所。<persName key="A004378">帝</persName>喜用之，俾掌樞務，權逾宰相，判廣<lb
ed="T" n="0834b13"/>平王府司馬事。<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>曰：「<persName key="A009805">卿</persName>為<persName key="A004378">朕</persName>師友。今父子<lb
ed="T" n="0834b14"/>三人資卿道義。」尋為<persName key="A012436">崔圓</persName>、<persName key="A008840">李輔國</persName>害其能，<persName key="A009805">泌</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0834b15"/>懼，乞遊<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡嶽</placeName>，詔許之。絕粒數年，遂見<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0834b16"/>焉。後終居相位，一如<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>之懸記矣。勅諡<persName key="A010199">大<lb
ed="T" n="0834b17"/>明禪師</persName>，塔存<placeName key="PL000000028928">嶽</placeName>中云。</p>
